      <title>日元兑欧元走弱，为出口商带来盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/yen-weakens-against-euro-providing-earnings-boost-for-exporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年迄今日元兑欧元已贬值约 9%，这为在欧洲销售量较大的日本公司带来了潜在的盈利增长。]]></description>
