      <title>蒙古为新主权财富基金挖掘矿业财富的计划辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/mongolia-defends-plan-to-tap-mining-riches-for-new-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙古总理为该国采矿法的修改进行辩护，此前外国投资者担心，这些修改可能会阻碍对蒙古大量关键矿产资源（包括用于电动汽车电池和其他新能源技术的矿产）的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/mongolia-defends-plan-to-tap-mining-riches-for-new-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 01:05:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
